{"pageContext":{"notebook":"AWS","section":"AWS EC2","page":{"id":"0-f2cd139b5200044f9fcf66109b72da9d!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2011","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-f2cd139b5200044f9fcf66109b72da9d!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2011","createdTime":"2017-08-29T15:01:51.88Z","title":"EC2에 EBS볼륨 마운트하기","createdByAppId":"","links":{"oneNoteEmbedUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!2000&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28AWS%20EC2.one%7Ca9db5ec1-48b3-a24e-bc07-98d85a74ce00%2FEC2%EC%97%90%20EBS%EB%B3%BC%EB%A5%A8%20%EB%A7%88%EC%9A%B4%ED%8A%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0%7C3d126e1d-a31f-c547-a94b-7c647a3abd4a%2F%29"},"oneNoteClientUrl":{"href":"onenote:https://d.docs.live.net/bc575ab8e2ab9833/Documents/AWS/AWS%20EC2.one#EC2%EC%97%90%20EBS%EB%B3%BC%EB%A5%A8%20%EB%A7%88%EC%9A%B4%ED%8A%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0&section-id=a9db5ec1-48b3-a24e-bc07-98d85a74ce00&page-id=3d126e1d-a31f-c547-a94b-7c647a3abd4a&end"},"oneNoteWebUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!2000&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28AWS%20EC2.one%7Ca9db5ec1-48b3-a24e-bc07-98d85a74ce00%2FEC2%EC%97%90%20EBS%EB%B3%BC%EB%A5%A8%20%EB%A7%88%EC%9A%B4%ED%8A%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0%7C3d126e1d-a31f-c547-a94b-7c647a3abd4a%2F%29"}},"contentUrl":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-f2cd139b5200044f9fcf66109b72da9d!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2011/content","lastModifiedTime":"2017-10-14T11:46:30Z","parentSection@odata.context":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/$metadata#me/notes/sections('0-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212011')/pages('0-f2cd139b5200044f9fcf66109b72da9d%211-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212011')/parentSection(id,name,self)/$entity","parentSection":{"id":"0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2011","name":"AWS EC2","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/sections/0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2011"},"content":"       http://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/ebs-using-volumes.html             $ lsblk￼: 사용가능한 디스크 디바이스 및 마운트포인트 확인     $ sudo file -s [device_name 경로] ￼: 파일 시스템 유형 확인￼2-1. Case 1￼    [ec2-user ~]$ sudo file -s /dev/xvdf￼   /dev/xvdf: data￼  이런 경우에는 파일 시스템이 없는경우이므로 파일시스템을 생성해야..￼    [ec2-user ~]$ sudo mkfs -t ext4 device_name￼2-2. Case 2￼    [ec2-user ~]$ sudo file -s /dev/xvda1￼/dev/xvda1: Linux rev 1.0 ext4 filesystem data, UUID=1701d228-e1bd-4094-a14c-8c64d6819362 (needs journal recovery) (extents) (large files) (huge files)￼  이런 경우는 다음단계로..     $ sudo mount [device_name 경로] [임의의 경로 || /mnt]￼: 목표 경로에다가 마운트하고자 하는 디바이스를 마운트한다.     $ df -h￼: 현재 마운트된 저장장치 목록을 확인한다.     $ lsblk￼: 마운트하기 전과 마운트 한 이후의 마운트포인트의 변화를 확인한다.           ","html":"\n\t\t<div style=\"position:absolute;left:48px;top:139px;width:642px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"http://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/ebs-using-volumes.html\">http://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/ebs-using-volumes.html</a></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<ol>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span lang=\"en-US\">$ lsblk&#xFFFC;: &#xC0AC;&#xC6A9;&#xAC00;&#xB2A5;&#xD55C; &#xB514;&#xC2A4;&#xD06C; &#xB514;&#xBC14;&#xC774;&#xC2A4; &#xBC0F; &#xB9C8;&#xC6B4;&#xD2B8;&#xD3EC;&#xC778;&#xD2B8; &#xD655;&#xC778;</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span lang=\"en-US\">$ sudo file -s [device_name &#xACBD;&#xB85C;] &#xFFFC;: &#xD30C;&#xC77C; &#xC2DC;&#xC2A4;&#xD15C; &#xC720;&#xD615; &#xD655;&#xC778;&#xFFFC;2-1. Case 1&#xFFFC;    <span style=\"font-family:Courier New;font-size:10.5pt;color:#444444;background-color:#f0f0f0\">[ec2-user ~]$ </span><span style=\"font-family:Courier New;font-size:10.5pt;color:#444444;background-color:#f0f0f0;font-weight:bold\">sudo file -s /dev/xvdf</span><span style=\"font-family:Courier New;font-size:10.5pt;color:#444444;background-color:#f0f0f0\">&#xFFFC;</span><span style=\"font-family:Courier New;font-size:10.5pt;color:#444444\">   </span><span style=\"font-family:Courier New;font-size:10.5pt;color:#444444;background-color:#f0f0f0\">/dev/xvdf: data</span>&#xFFFC;  &#xC774;&#xB7F0; &#xACBD;&#xC6B0;&#xC5D0;&#xB294; &#xD30C;&#xC77C; &#xC2DC;&#xC2A4;&#xD15C;&#xC774; &#xC5C6;&#xB294;&#xACBD;&#xC6B0;&#xC774;&#xBBC0;&#xB85C; &#xD30C;&#xC77C;&#xC2DC;&#xC2A4;&#xD15C;&#xC744; &#xC0DD;&#xC131;&#xD574;&#xC57C;..&#xFFFC;    <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Courier New;font-size:10.5pt;color:#444444;background-color:#f0f0f0\">[ec2-user ~]$ </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Courier New;font-size:10.5pt;color:#444444;background-color:#f0f0f0;font-weight:bold\">sudo mkfs -t ext4 </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Courier New;font-size:10.5pt;color:red;background-color:#f0f0f0;font-weight:bold;font-style:italic\">device_name</span>&#xFFFC;2-2. Case 2&#xFFFC;    <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Courier New;font-size:10.5pt;color:#444444;background-color:#f0f0f0\">[ec2-user ~]$ </span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Courier New;font-size:10.5pt;color:#444444;background-color:#f0f0f0;font-weight:bold\">sudo file -s /dev/xvda1</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Courier New;font-size:10.5pt;color:#444444;background-color:#f0f0f0\">&#xFFFC;</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Courier New;font-size:10.5pt;color:#444444;background-color:#f0f0f0\">/dev/xvda1: Linux rev 1.0 ext4 filesystem data, UUID=1701d228-e1bd-4094-a14c-8c64d6819362 (needs journal recovery) (extents) (large files) (huge files)</span>&#xFFFC;  &#xC774;&#xB7F0; &#xACBD;&#xC6B0;&#xB294; &#xB2E4;&#xC74C;&#xB2E8;&#xACC4;&#xB85C;..</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span lang=\"en-US\">$ sudo mount [device_name &#xACBD;&#xB85C;] [&#xC784;&#xC758;&#xC758; &#xACBD;&#xB85C; || /mnt]&#xFFFC;: &#xBAA9;&#xD45C; &#xACBD;&#xB85C;&#xC5D0;&#xB2E4;&#xAC00; &#xB9C8;&#xC6B4;&#xD2B8;&#xD558;&#xACE0;&#xC790; &#xD558;&#xB294; &#xB514;&#xBC14;&#xC774;&#xC2A4;&#xB97C; &#xB9C8;&#xC6B4;&#xD2B8;&#xD55C;&#xB2E4;.</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span lang=\"en-US\">$ df -h&#xFFFC;: &#xD604;&#xC7AC; &#xB9C8;&#xC6B4;&#xD2B8;&#xB41C; &#xC800;&#xC7A5;&#xC7A5;&#xCE58; &#xBAA9;&#xB85D;&#xC744; &#xD655;&#xC778;&#xD55C;&#xB2E4;.</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span lang=\"en-US\">$ lsblk&#xFFFC;: &#xB9C8;&#xC6B4;&#xD2B8;&#xD558;&#xAE30; &#xC804;&#xACFC; &#xB9C8;&#xC6B4;&#xD2B8; &#xD55C; &#xC774;&#xD6C4;&#xC758; &#xB9C8;&#xC6B4;&#xD2B8;&#xD3EC;&#xC778;&#xD2B8;&#xC758; &#xBCC0;&#xD654;&#xB97C; &#xD655;&#xC778;&#xD55C;&#xB2E4;.</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\n\n"}}}